Dialogue: 5,0:00:42.98,0:00:44.77,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 5,0:00:47.19,0:00:49.57,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,You did this?
Dialogue: 5,0:00:53.07,0:00:55.03,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,You killed them all?!{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:00:58.24,0:00:59.99,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,I didn't kill them.
Dialogue: 5,0:00:59.99,0:01:00.74,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Liar!
Dialogue: 5,0:01:00.74,0:01:02.33,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,I'm not lying.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:02.87,0:01:06.42,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,People killing one another is now a thing of the past.{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:01:06.42,0:01:08.84,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,All I did was get them to stop moving.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:10.38,0:01:12.88,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,{\i1\fs54}Killing{\i0\fs55} them is the job of a gravekeeper.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:31.77,0:01:36.49,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,I was seven when my mother died.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:38.16,0:01:40.74,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Without her, I was all alone,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:40.74,0:01:42.91,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,but then the villagers told me...
Dialogue: 5,0:01:44.58,0:01:48.04,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,Ai, starting today, you're a gravekeeper.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:48.37,0:01:53.05,Default,Villagers,0,0,0,,Lady Alfa was a splendid gravekeeper.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:51.75,0:01:56.13,Default BG,Villagers,0,0,0,,We need a gravekeeper.
Dialogue: 5,0:01:54.59,0:01:57.09,Default,Villagers,0,0,0,,As the last of her bloodline,
Dialogue: 5,0:01:57.09,0:02:00.01,Default,Villagers,0,0,0,,only you can take her place, Ai.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:01.64,0:02:03.14,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:08.39,0:02:10.52,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,That's right, Ai.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:14.65,0:02:16.99,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Become a gravekeeper?
Dialogue: 5,0:02:18.91,0:02:23.49,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,That day, I became this village's gravekeeper.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:25.16,0:02:29.79,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Since my mother passed away, none of the villagers have died.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:30.63,0:02:34.92,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,But each day, I've been digging grave after grave.
Dialogue: 5,0:02:36.09,0:02:39.76,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,After all, I'm a gravekeeper!
