Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.23,0:04:23.40,Nichiyoubi,Typesetting,0,0,18,,{\fad(300,0)\an8\blur0.6\fscx38\fscy56}God created the world on a Monday.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:19.69,0:04:23.40,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,God created the world on a Monday.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.07,0:04:30.24,Nichiyoubi,Typesetting,0,0,18,,{\fad(300,0)\an8\blur0.6\fscx38\fscy56}On Tuesday, He drew the line between Order and Chaos.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:26.53,0:04:30.24,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,On Tuesday, He drew the line between Order and Chaos.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.41,0:04:37.08,Nichiyoubi,Typesetting,0,0,18,,{\fad(300,0)\an8\blur0.6\fscx38\fscy56}On Wednesday, He arranged each and every number.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:32.91,0:04:37.08,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,On Wednesday, He arranged each and every number.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.79,0:04:42.92,Nichiyoubi,Typesetting,0,0,18,,{\fad(255,0)\an8\blur0.6\fscx38\fscy56}On Thursday, He permitted the ebb and flow of Time.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:39.34,0:04:42.92,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,On Thursday, He permitted the ebb and flow of Time.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:44.18,0:04:45.43,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,That's it for today, everyone.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:46.51,0:04:47.60,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Until tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:52.93,Nichiyoubi,Typesetting,0,0,18,,{\fad(255,0)\an8\blur0.6\fscx38\fscy56}On Friday, God explored every nook and cranny of the world.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:49.01,0:04:52.93,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,{\q2}On Friday, God explored every nook and cranny of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.40,0:04:59.52,Nichiyoubi,Typesetting,0,0,18,,{\fad(255,0)\an8\blur0.6\fscx38\fscy56}On Saturday, He rested.
Dialogue: 5,0:04:56.90,0:04:59.52,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,On Saturday, He rested.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.90,0:05:07.28,Nichiyoubi,Typesetting,0,0,18,,{\fad(300,0)\an8\blur3.5\fscx38\fscy56\c&H000000&}And on Sunday, God...
Dialogue: 1,0:05:03.90,0:05:07.28,Nichiyoubi,Typesetting,0,0,18,,{\fad(300,0)\an8\blur0.6\fscx38\fscy56}And on Sunday, God...
Dialogue: 5,0:05:04.57,0:05:07.28,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,And on Sunday, God...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.03,0:05:10.79,Nichiyoubi,Typesetting,0,0,18,,{\an8\blur0.6\fscx38\fscy56}forsook the world.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:16.25,0:05:18.08,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,"Heaven and Hell are too crowded."
Dialogue: 5,0:05:19.34,0:05:21.38,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,"It won't be long before this world is, too."
Dialogue: 5,0:05:22.71,0:05:24.42,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,"Ah, I have failed."
Dialogue: 5,0:05:25.38,0:05:28.76,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,When God abandoned the world, leaving behind only those words,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:28.76,0:05:31.01,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,people stopped dying.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:32.43,0:05:34.48,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Even as their hearts stopped beating,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:35.31,0:05:36.81,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,even as their flesh rotted,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:37.94,0:05:40.94,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,the dead kept moving.{crawling/squirming}
Dialogue: 5,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.61,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,It is said that in order to save those very people,
Dialogue: 5,0:05:46.61,0:05:50.20,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,God sent to this world one final miracle:
Dialogue: 5,0:05:50.20,0:05:52.12,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,the gravekeepers.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:53.74,0:05:55.91,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,It's time, Ai.
Dialogue: 5,0:05:56.96,0:05:59.50,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Grant Lady Alfa a peaceful slumber.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:01.38,0:06:03.30,Default,Yohki,0,0,0,,You're the only one who can do it.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:05.34,0:06:06.22,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:09.39,0:06:14.39,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Only burials by gravekeepers{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:15.35,0:06:18.89,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,can grant a peaceful slumber for the restless dead.{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:06:28.70,0:06:29.86,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Perfect!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:30.78,0:06:35.49,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,I am clearly an excellent and dignified gravekeeper!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:37.58,0:06:39.12,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,Heeey!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:40.37,0:06:41.96,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:42.88,0:06:44.67,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Mr. Yuuto...
Dialogue: 5,0:06:45.92,0:06:48.17,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Come on, Ai! Stay dignified!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:50.68,0:06:54.01,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,Hey, everyone, Ai's back!
Dialogue: 5,0:06:55.64,0:06:59.02,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,I greet you all as gravekeeper.
Dialogue: 5,0:06:59.52,0:07:01.90,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,May your lives continue—
Dialogue: 5,0:07:00.27,0:07:01.60,Default BG,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,You're late.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:01.60,0:07:02.69,Default BG,Villagers,0,0,0,,Are you hungry?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:02.69,0:07:03.90,Default BG,Villagers,0,0,0,,We brought cookies.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:03.90,0:07:04.98,Default BG,Villagers,0,0,0,,I baked some muffins!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:04.98,0:07:06.73,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Uh, everyone...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:04.98,0:07:07.32,Default BG,Villagers,0,0,0,,The lemonade's ice-cold!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:06.73,0:07:08.15,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:08.15,0:07:10.57,Default,Yohki,0,0,0,,Hey! What do you all think you're doing?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:11.07,0:07:14.91,Default,Yohki,0,0,0,,How many times must I tell you to stop feeding the gravekeeper?!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:16.54,0:07:19.21,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,Well... you see...
Dialogue: 5,0:07:19.71,0:07:21.62,Default,Yohki,0,0,0,,Well, Ai?
Dialogue: 5,0:07:23.17,0:07:25.63,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,I dried do zdop dem!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:25.96,0:07:27.38,Default,Yohki,0,0,0,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:30.09,0:07:31.63,Default,Yohki,0,0,0,,Let's head home, Ai.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:33.18,0:07:34.51,Default,Yohki,0,0,0,,Anna's waiting for us.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:36.26,0:07:38.22,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Ogay. Fanks.{re: Good worg. It seems really weird to me to say "Good work" here. I think she's saying something like "Thanks for coming to pick me up," but even "Thanks" by itself is weird.}
Dialogue: 5,0:07:39.60,0:07:41.69,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Well, ebryone,
Dialogue: 5,0:07:41.69,0:07:43.10,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,take care!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:43.10,0:07:45.19,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,See you tomorrow, Ai.
Dialogue: 5,0:07:45.19,0:07:47.36,Default,Villagers,0,0,0,,Thanks for always giving it your best!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:50.57,0:07:52.07,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Anna!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:52.07,0:07:53.03,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:53.82,0:07:55.45,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,I'm home!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:56.62,0:07:58.49,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Now, now, Ai!
Dialogue: 5,0:07:59.16,0:08:00.29,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:02.96,0:08:05.17,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Anna, you stink.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:06.34,0:08:07.63,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Ai!
Dialogue: 5,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.63,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,It's just perfume.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:09.63,0:08:11.88,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,I don't see why you wear that stuff.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:11.88,0:08:14.34,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,I like your natural scent.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:16.22,0:08:19.68,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Well, I'm sure you'll understand \Nthe ways of us adults when you become one.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:20.85,0:08:23.56,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,That's what you all say.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:25.60,0:08:30.90,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,After my mother died, Yohki and Anna took me in.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:31.53,0:08:36.12,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,My real father is out there somewhere.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:37.12,0:08:39.74,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,His name's Humpnie Humbert.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:41.00,0:08:45.25,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,My mother told me he'd come see me someday.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:51.59,0:08:53.63,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,This is so painful sometimes.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:55.05,0:08:56.89,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,She's only twelve years old.
Dialogue: 5,0:08:57.43,0:08:59.22,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,She's just a child,
Dialogue: 5,0:08:59.22,0:09:01.85,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,and we're putting the weight \Nof the world on her shoulders.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:02.68,0:09:03.64,Default,Yohki,0,0,0,,Anna.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:04.52,0:09:07.86,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I truly am happy we took her in.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:08.69,0:09:11.94,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,Having a child in this day and age \Nis like a dream come true.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:13.15,0:09:13.94,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:15.99,0:09:18.12,Default,Anna,0,0,0,,I wonder if {\i1\fs54}she's{\i0\fs55} happy.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:26.62,0:09:28.75,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,I wonder why sometimes...
Dialogue: 5,0:09:30.25,0:09:35.26,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Yohki and Anna look at me with really sad faces.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:36.97,0:09:38.80,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Why would that be?
Dialogue: 5,0:09:39.47,0:09:42.81,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,It sometimes feels like they're keeping something from me.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:46.52,0:09:47.48,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,I'm finished!
Dialogue: 5,0:09:48.40,0:09:50.31,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Forty-seven in all.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:51.32,0:09:55.03,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,I went and dug enough graves \Nfor everyone in the village.
Dialogue: 5,0:09:56.45,0:09:59.62,Default Italics,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,What will there be to do starting tomorrow?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:05.00,0:10:08.62,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Guess I could always go and help everyone out.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:13.80,0:10:14.71,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:18.47,0:10:21.35,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Where is everyone?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:24.81,0:10:26.48,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,I wonder what could've happened.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:30.94,0:10:31.98,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Whoa.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:43.78,0:10:44.49,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:44.87,0:10:48.66,Default,Marker,0,0,0,,{part b maybe?}
Dialogue: 5,0:10:52.38,0:10:53.25,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 5,0:10:55.80,0:10:57.01,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Do you live here?
Dialogue: 5,0:10:59.34,0:11:00.38,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Are you by yourself?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:04.30,0:11:06.68,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Can you talk, or are you dumb?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:06.68,0:11:08.52,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,I-I can talk!
Dialogue: 5,0:11:08.52,0:11:10.19,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Good for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:11.56,0:11:13.15,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,So, who are you?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:13.15,0:11:16.15,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,I'm Ai, the gravekeeper.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:17.36,0:11:18.24,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Oh?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:20.53,0:11:22.28,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:22.28,0:11:23.66,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,You?{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:23.66,0:11:25.20,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,You're the gravekeeper here?{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:11:28.04,0:11:30.21,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Is there a problem with that?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:31.25,0:11:32.37,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,No, not really.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:33.42,0:11:36.05,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Guess I might as well.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:40.51,0:11:42.38,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,There's something I must ask a gravekeeper about.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:42.76,0:11:43.80,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,May I?
Dialogue: 5,0:11:43.80,0:11:44.80,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 5,0:11:44.80,0:11:45.89,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:46.43,0:11:48.06,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Query:
Dialogue: 5,0:11:49.89,0:11:54.19,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,I would like information on one called or one who calls herself "Hana."
Dialogue: 5,0:11:54.19,0:11:55.90,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,I'm not asking whether she's dead or alive.
Dialogue: 5,0:11:55.90,0:11:59.15,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Well... I'm not sure.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:01.11,0:12:02.40,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Supplemental query:
Dialogue: 5,0:12:03.11,0:12:06.07,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,I would like information on a woman \Nwho matches the following description.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:06.49,0:12:07.95,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Um...?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:07.95,0:12:09.58,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Between thirty and forty years of age.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:09.58,0:12:11.16,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Brown hair. Black eyes.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.62,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Distinct facial features.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:13.17,0:12:15.83,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Approximately my height. Flat-chested.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:15.83,0:12:17.75,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Again, whether she's dead or alive is irrelevant.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:18.46,0:12:20.76,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Um, well...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:21.38,0:12:24.09,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,I think Anna's around that age,
Dialogue: 5,0:12:24.09,0:12:26.30,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,but she's not flat-chested.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:26.30,0:12:28.39,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,And Yohki's a guy.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:29.01,0:12:31.52,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Hmm...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:34.14,0:12:35.48,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Not here either, huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:36.94,0:12:38.36,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,H-Hold—
Dialogue: 5,0:12:38.36,0:12:40.15,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:42.90,0:12:43.99,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:12:43.99,0:12:45.41,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,I'm a busy man, you know.
Dialogue: 5,0:12:45.74,0:12:46.62,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:47.16,0:12:49.41,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Well, uh...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:51.58,0:12:52.45,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:12:53.33,0:12:55.42,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Y-You're very handsome!
Dialogue: 5,0:12:58.34,0:12:59.42,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:00.21,0:13:01.21,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Later.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:01.21,0:13:01.96,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:03.72,0:13:05.13,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Anything else?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:05.13,0:13:06.13,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:06.68,0:13:07.89,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Uh...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:07.89,0:13:08.93,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Are you...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:09.26,0:13:11.01,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:11.01,0:13:12.52,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Who are you?{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:13.18,0:13:14.06,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:14.77,0:13:15.77,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Well, all right.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:16.56,0:13:17.27,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,I...
Dialogue: 5,0:13:19.77,0:13:23.03,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,I am the Man-Eating Toy, Humpnie Humbert.{PV}
Dialogue: 5,0:13:26.53,0:13:27.16,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:27.16,0:13:28.91,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,You have the same name as my father!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:29.32,0:13:30.24,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:30.24,0:13:31.33,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,It all makes sense!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:31.79,0:13:34.62,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,So you're Humpnie Humbert!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:34.62,0:13:37.29,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Now hold it right there.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:37.29,0:13:39.79,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Who the hell would have that kind of name?!
Dialogue: 5,0:13:40.38,0:13:43.26,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,But that's my father's name.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:43.26,0:13:44.34,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:44.34,0:13:45.63,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,You have parents?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:45.63,0:13:47.01,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,So, what?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:47.51,0:13:49.72,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Your dad's name is Humpnie Humbert?
Dialogue: 5,0:13:49.72,0:13:50.47,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:50.47,0:13:52.64,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,My mother told me
Dialogue: 5,0:13:53.56,0:13:56.69,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,that he'd surely come see me someday.
Dialogue: 5,0:13:58.15,0:14:00.36,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Father? Father, is that you?!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:00.94,0:14:01.77,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:02.57,0:14:05.78,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Do I look like I could be your dad?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:06.15,0:14:08.20,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,I must admit it is a little strange.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:08.66,0:14:09.62,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:09.62,0:14:14.49,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,In my mind, my father's always been \Nthis tough guy around forty years old.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:15.04,0:14:15.54,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:16.04,0:14:21.04,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,And it'd be strange if he didn't show up \Nletting out some fierce battle cry.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:28.38,0:14:31.35,Default Italics,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,There are much stranger things about this situation.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:31.35,0:14:34.85,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,But those are just minor issues!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:34.85,0:14:37.10,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Nope, you've definitely got big issues.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:37.56,0:14:39.65,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,You're still my father!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:40.15,0:14:40.90,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,And why's that?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:42.19,0:14:43.32,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Just intuition!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:43.82,0:14:45.40,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,We were fated to meet!
Dialogue: 5,0:14:46.11,0:14:49.03,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,You have no intention of holding a conversation with me, do you?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:49.03,0:14:50.82,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Of course I do,
Dialogue: 5,0:14:50.82,0:14:51.78,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Father.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:55.62,0:14:58.33,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Hey, you're a gravekeeper, right?
Dialogue: 5,0:14:58.33,0:14:59.12,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Yup.
Dialogue: 5,0:14:59.71,0:15:02.29,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,In that case, I have a job request for you.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:03.00,0:15:04.80,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:05.46,0:15:08.80,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,There's only one thing it could be.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:10.72,0:15:11.43,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:26.69,0:15:27.98,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:28.44,0:15:29.74,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Everyone!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:35.08,0:15:37.45,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Yohki. Anna.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:37.91,0:15:38.79,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,This can't be.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:39.54,0:15:40.79,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,This can't be happening!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:44.63,0:15:46.67,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,If it isn't Ai!
Dialogue: 5,0:15:47.75,0:15:50.30,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Mr. Yuuto...?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:50.92,0:15:53.55,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,You okay, Ai?
Dialogue: 5,0:15:53.89,0:15:55.35,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Mister...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:55.97,0:15:56.93,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,There's...
Dialogue: 5,0:15:56.93,0:15:59.22,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,a big wound on your head.
Dialogue: 5,0:15:59.64,0:16:02.73,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,Oh, this? This is nothing.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:03.35,0:16:04.81,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,It doesn't even hurt.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:05.73,0:16:06.73,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:06.73,0:16:08.78,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,There's big trouble!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:08.78,0:16:11.24,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,Er, what was it again?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:11.24,0:16:12.86,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,Anyway, we're in trouble!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:12.86,0:16:15.28,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,W-We've gotta run away!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:20.95,0:16:22.71,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Ai?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:24.92,0:16:26.33,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:27.88,0:16:30.05,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,Why are you staring at me like that?
Dialogue: 5,0:16:33.26,0:16:33.88,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,Stop it!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:33.88,0:16:37.47,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,What's the matter with you? \NYou're staring at me like I'm some kind of monster!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:38.10,0:16:40.22,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,I'm still the same!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:41.14,0:16:42.10,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,No, you're not!
Dialogue: 5,0:16:55.91,0:16:57.70,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,Ai, stay down.
Dialogue: 5,0:16:57.95,0:16:59.41,Default,Mr. Yuuto,0,0,0,,It's that punk again.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:00.79,0:17:03.04,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Hey, you! Undead monster!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:04.62,0:17:10.34,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,You've got three seconds before I unload thirty rounds of lead in that direction.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:11.21,0:17:12.63,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Two seconds!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:13.88,0:17:14.76,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,One!
Dialogue: 5,0:17:18.47,0:17:20.35,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,A splendid display of character.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:38.07,0:17:38.82,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:39.32,0:17:41.33,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,I should've finished him off earlier.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:41.33,0:17:46.58,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Not to worry. I blew the rest of their heads clean off.
Dialogue: 5,0:17:52.09,0:17:53.26,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 5,0:17:56.42,0:17:58.64,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,You did this?
Dialogue: 5,0:17:59.14,0:18:00.72,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,You killed them all?!{pv}
Dialogue: 5,0:18:04.39,0:18:05.93,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,I didn't kill them.
Dialogue: 5,0:18:31.42,0:18:32.84,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,What have you...
Dialogue: 5,0:18:32.84,0:18:33.84,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:34.50,0:18:35.46,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,How could you?
Dialogue: 5,0:18:37.84,0:18:39.59,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,You're not my father!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:40.51,0:18:43.10,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,My father would never do something like this!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:43.72,0:18:47.23,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,You cannot be my father!
Dialogue: 5,0:18:49.90,0:18:51.94,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Haven't I been saying that from the beginning?
Dialogue: 5,0:19:02.32,0:19:03.62,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Come with me.
Dialogue: 5,0:19:09.37,0:19:10.54,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Bury them.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:03.64,0:20:05.51,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,How long do you plan on following me around?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:07.18,0:20:08.01,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:08.01,0:20:10.98,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,More importantly, what do you plan on doing from now on?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:13.02,0:20:15.27,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Well, I'm a gravekeeper.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:18.69,0:20:20.40,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,You're no gravekeeper.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:22.86,0:20:26.74,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,At first, I thought maybe \Nthat asshole of a God could've indeed
Dialogue: 5,0:20:26.74,0:20:30.54,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,made a weirdo like you a gravekeeper,
Dialogue: 5,0:20:30.54,0:20:31.71,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,but I was wrong.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:32.16,0:20:34.58,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,But my mother was—
Dialogue: 5,0:20:34.58,0:20:35.79,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Let's start with that.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:36.63,0:20:38.21,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Gravekeepers don't have parents.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:38.21,0:20:38.88,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:39.34,0:20:43.30,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,They tend to show up out of nowhere, like flies.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:43.97,0:20:45.64,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,They couldn't possibly have parents.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:45.64,0:20:48.85,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,But everyone in the village—
Dialogue: 5,0:20:48.85,0:20:50.89,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Called you a gravekeeper?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:50.89,0:20:52.81,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,That's pretty flimsy proof.
Dialogue: 5,0:20:53.31,0:20:55.90,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Didn't you consider that \Nthey could've been lying to you?
Dialogue: 5,0:20:57.23,0:20:58.52,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,But that...
Dialogue: 5,0:20:58.52,0:20:59.86,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,No, it can't be!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:01.69,0:21:04.78,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,My mother was Alfa, the gravekeeper,
Dialogue: 5,0:21:04.78,0:21:07.41,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,and my father's name is Humpnie Humbert—
Dialogue: 5,0:21:07.41,0:21:08.28,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,Listen.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:08.28,0:21:11.66,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,"Humpnie Humbert" is just a fairy tale.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:12.37,0:21:16.04,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,It's the name of a toy \Nthat keeps moving even without a spring.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:16.62,0:21:19.04,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,I only borrowed the name from that fairy tale.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:20.00,0:21:22.34,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,I bet your mother did the same thing.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:22.34,0:21:25.18,Default,Ai Astin,0,0,0,,Th-That's a lie!
Dialogue: 5,0:21:25.18,0:21:27.97,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,I wonder what the villagers here were trying to do.
Dialogue: 5,0:21:28.47,0:21:31.60,Default,Humpnie Humbert,0,0,0,,They convinced a little kid like you that she was a gravekeeper
